OL,3,CLocal elections Midlands: What next?
OL,5,FSuddenly local elections become less
OL,6,Fabout bins and potholes and so much
OL,7,Fmore about the future of politics on a
OL,8,Fgrander scale.
OL,10,FThe narrative across the Midlands has
OL,11,Fbeen the rise of Reform UK. Some
OL,12,Fspectacular gains - the first big win
OL,13,Fof the night at Newcastle Under Lyme -
OL,14,Fan area that so often reflects the
OL,15,Fnational mood. Of the 44 seats up for
OL,16,Fgrabs Reform secured 27 - from a
OL,17,Fstarting point of just one.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
