OL,3,CLocal elections Midlands: What next?
OL,5,FThere were big losses for Labour in
OL,6,FBirmingham where an exclusive ITV News
OL,7,FCentral poll had predicted the party
OL,8,Fwould be punished severely - partly
OL,9,Fthe backlash against the national
OL,10,Fgovernment but also the frustration
OL,11,Fover the long bins strike.
OL,13,FCouncil leader John Cotton lost his
OL,14,Fseat. He had of course been promising
OL,15,Fthat a strike deal would be 'within
OL,16,Freach' if Labour were returned to
OL,17,Fpower.
OL,19,FLosses too in the other Labour
OL,20,Fmetropolitan strongholds of Sandwell
OL,21,Fand Coventry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
